<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>ENT CMJLF — 500</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Libre+Baskerville:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style>
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
:root{
  --green:#113B26;--green2:#166534;--green3:#1a7340;
  --leaf:#22C55E;--gold:#D97706;
  --white:#FDFCFA;--fog:#E8F0E8;--rule:#C8D9C8;
  --ink:#1A1612;--mid:#5a7060;
  --ease:cubic-bezier(.25,.46,.45,.94);
}
html{-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased}
body{
  font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;
  background:var(--green);
  min-height:100vh;
  display:flex;flex-direction:column;
  position:relative;overflow:hidden;
}

/* ── Cercles décoratifs subtils ── */
body::before{
  content:'';position:fixed;
  width:600px;height:600px;border-radius:50%;
  background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(34,197,94,.08) 0%,transparent 70%);
  top:-150px;right:-150px;pointer-events:none;
}
body::after{
  content:'';position:fixed;
  width:400px;height:400px;border-radius:50%;
  background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(255,255,255,.04) 0%,transparent 70%);
  bottom:-100px;left:-100px;pointer-events:none;
}

/* ── NAV ── */
nav{
  position:relative;z-index:2;
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;
  padding:22px 56px;
  border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
}
.nav-brand{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;text-decoration:none}
.nav-logo{
  width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:50%;
  border:1.5px solid rgba(212,168,83,.35);
  object-fit:cover;background:#fff;
}
.nav-name{font-family:'Libre Baskerville',serif;font-size:13px;color:#fff;font-weight:700;line-height:1.2}
.nav-sub{font-size:9px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.3);letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase}
.nav-btn{
  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;
  font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:rgba(255,255,255,.6);
  text-decoration:none;
  border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.13);border-radius:5px;
  padding:8px 16px;transition:all .22s;
}
.nav-btn:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.07);color:#fff}
.nav-btn svg{width:12px;height:12px}

/* ── MAIN ── */
main{
  flex:1;position:relative;z-index:1;
  display:flex;flex-direction:column;
  align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  text-align:center;padding:60px 32px;
}

/* Code grand en filigrane */
.err-bg-num{
  position:absolute;
  font-family:'Libre Baskerville',serif;
  font-size:clamp(140px,22vw,260px);
  font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-.05em;
  color:rgba(255,255,255,.04);
  line-height:1;user-select:none;pointer-events:none;
  top:50%;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);
  white-space:nowrap;
}

/* Icône */
.err-icon{
  width:72px;height:72px;border-radius:50%;
  background:rgba(255,255,255,.06);
  border:1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  margin:0 auto 24px;
  animation:fadeUp .6s .1s var(--ease) both;
}
.err-icon svg{width:28px;height:28px;color:var(--gold)}

/* Chip */
.err-chip{
  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;
  background:rgba(255,255,255,.06);
  border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);
  border-radius:4px;padding:5px 13px;
  font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;
  color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);margin-bottom:18px;
  animation:fadeUp .6s .18s var(--ease) both;
}
.chip-dot{width:5px;height:5px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--gold)}

/* Règle */
.err-rule{
  width:32px;height:2px;background:var(--gold);
  margin:16px auto 20px;
  transform-origin:center;
  animation:grow .5s .3s var(--ease) both;
}
@keyframes grow{from{transform:scaleX(0)}to{transform:scaleX(1)}}

/* Titre */
.err-title{
  font-family:'Libre Baskerville',serif;
  font-size:clamp(24px,4vw,42px);
  color:#fff;line-height:1.1;margin-bottom:14px;
  animation:fadeUp .6s .28s var(--ease) both;
}
.err-title em{font-style:italic;color:var(--gold)}

/* Description */
.err-desc{
  font-size:15px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.42);
  line-height:1.75;max-width:440px;margin:0 auto 36px;
  animation:fadeUp .6s .36s var(--ease) both;
}

/* Boutons */
.err-btns{
  display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;
  animation:fadeUp .6s .44s var(--ease) both;
}
.btn-white{
  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;
  padding:13px 26px;border-radius:6px;
  font-size:13px;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;
  background:var(--white);color:var(--green);
  box-shadow:0 4px 18px rgba(0,0,0,.2);
  transition:all .28s var(--ease);
}
.btn-white:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.28)}
.btn-white svg{width:14px;height:14px}
.btn-outline{
  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;
  padding:12px 22px;border-radius:6px;
  font-size:13px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;
  background:transparent;border:1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,.15);
  color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);
  transition:all .25s;
}
.btn-outline:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.08);color:#fff;transform:translateY(-1px)}
.btn-outline svg{width:14px;height:14px}

/* ── FOOTER ── */
footer{
  position:relative;z-index:2;
  padding:18px 56px;
  border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.07);
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;
  flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px;
}
.foot-copy{font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.2);letter-spacing:.05em}
.foot-ents{display:flex;gap:14px}
.fent{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;font-size:10px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.18);font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.06em}
.fent-dot{width:5px;height:5px;border-radius:50%}
.fdg{background:#22C55E}.fdb{background:#D97706}.fdc{background:#4ADE80}

@keyframes fadeUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(14px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}

@media(max-width:700px){
  nav,footer{padding:14px 20px}
  .err-btns{flex-direction:column;align-items:center}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<nav>
  <a href="/personnel/accueil" class="nav-brand">
    <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="CMJLF" class="nav-logo"/>
    <div><div class="nav-name">ENT — CMJLF</div><div class="nav-sub">Portail Numérique</div></div>
  </a>
  <a href="/personnel/accueil" class="nav-btn">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/><polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/></svg>
    Accueil
  </a>
</nav>
<main>
  <div class="err-bg-num">500</div>
  <div class="err-icon">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg>
  </div>
  <div class="err-chip"><span class="chip-dot"></span>Erreur serveur</div>
  <div class="err-rule"></div>
  <h1 class="err-title">Erreur <em>interne</em> du serveur</h1>
  <p class="err-desc">Une erreur inattendue s'est produite. Notre équipe technique a été notifiée et travaille à la résolution. Réessayez dans un instant.</p>
  <div class="err-btns">
    <a href="/personnel/accueil" class="btn-white">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/><polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/></svg>
      Retour à l'accueil
    </a>
    <a href="javascript:location.reload()" class="btn-outline"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="1 4 1 10 7 10"/><path d="M3.51 15a9 9 0 1 0 .49-4.5"/></svg>Réessayer</a>
  </div>
</main>
<footer>
  <span class="foot-copy">© 2025 Groupe Scolaire Jean de la Fontaine — Dakar</span>
  <div class="foot-ents">
    <div class="fent"><span class="fent-dot fdg"></span>UAHB</div>
    <div class="fent"><span class="fent-dot fdb"></span>CMJLF</div>
    <div class="fent"><span class="fent-dot fdc"></span>CTD</div>
  </div>
</footer>
</body>
</html>